            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>lemony smoked basa & spinach gluten free linguine</strong> and top with the <strong>lemon zest</strong> and a generous grind of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Drizzle with <strong>olive oil</strong> and garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
